    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《驾驶难》中挑战自我！驾驶一辆装有轮子的浴缸，穿越陡峭、险恶的地形，每一次失误都会让你前功尽弃。掌握艰难的物理驱动玩法，磨练自己的耐心，跟随杰夫的经历自我怀疑、家庭冲突和情感的成长之旅，最终找到勇敢、自我接纳的力量，以及对未来的希望。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/1aa1cb5c00e0c09277e5d61bff34d39d.poster.avif?t=1755091142\" width=628 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/1aa1cb5c00e0c09277e5d61bff34d39d.webm?t=1755091142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/1aa1cb5c00e0c09277e5d61bff34d39d.mp4?t=1755091142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶浴缸： 控制杰夫驾驶一辆装有轮子的物理浴缸。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择您的体验：轻松模式享受悠闲乐趣，或困难模式迎接原始挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索7个世界： 每个世界都有独特的挑战与游戏机制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >易上手，难精通： 简单的控制方法，充满挑战的机制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >情感旅程： 杰夫直面父亲的期待，找到属于自己的道路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可定制浴缸： 解锁并使用不同的浴缸车辆皮肤。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集肥皂： 在游戏中找到21块肥皂。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >警告！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款高难度的游戏将考验你的耐心——失误是挑战的一部分。当困难来临时，您是会坚持不懈还是选择放弃？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/cf7a8c69af4838936ed5f611a1934114.poster.avif?t=1755091142\" width=628 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/cf7a8c69af4838936ed5f611a1934114.webm?t=1755091142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/cf7a8c69af4838936ed5f611a1934114.mp4?t=1755091142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入官方讨论QQ群：1025388726</p>",
